<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yīn zhe yé sū ài de yuán gù 迦南420</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yīn zhe yé sū ài de yuán gù wǒ men yǒng gǎn huó zhe
 yīn zhe líng hún xū qiú de yuán gù wǒ men jiān qiáng huó zhe
 bù pà cuò zhé hé dǎ jī fēng yǔ liàn zhēng gǔ
 yǔ shī yī xuě jī shēn bù shuō lèi hé kǔ
 wǒ men shì jī dū tú yī shēng yào fú shì zhǔ
 shì rén zài guān kàn tiān shǐ yě jì lù
 wǒ men shì jī dū tú shēng lái bù pà kǔ
 zǒu guò xiǎo xiǎo cūn luò wān wān shān lù.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>420</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>